<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q30_v8" title="Q30_v8" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float"><qti-default-value><qti-value>0</qti-value></qti-default-value></qti-outcome-declaration><qti-item-body>
    <p>En ciertas estructuras hechas con barras metálicas, se observa que el número de paneles planos (caras), más el número de uniones (vértices), es igual al número de barras (aristas) más 2. Esta relación se puede escribir como:
      <m:math>
        <m:mi>C</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mi>V</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mi>A</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn>
      </m:math>
    </p>
    <p>Una de estas estructuras tiene 10 uniones y 22 barras y cumple con la relación descrita. ¿Cuántos paneles planos (caras) tiene?</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">10<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si <m:math><m:mi>C</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:math>, entonces <m:math><m:mi>C</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mi>V</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>20</m:mn></m:math>, pero <m:math><m:mi>A</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>22</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>24</m:mn></m:math>. Como <m:math><m:mn>20</m:mn><m:mo>≠</m:mo><m:mn>24</m:mn></m:math>, esta opción no cumple la relación.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">14<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Reemplazando <m:math><m:mi>V</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:math> y <m:math><m:mi>A</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>22</m:mn></m:math> en <m:math><m:mi>C</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mi>V</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mi>A</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:math>, se obtiene <m:math><m:mi>C</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>22</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>24</m:mn></m:math>. Entonces <m:math><m:mi>C</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>24</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>14</m:mn></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">12<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si <m:math><m:mi>C</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>12</m:mn></m:math>, entonces <m:math><m:mi>C</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mi>V</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>12</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>22</m:mn></m:math>, pero <m:math><m:mi>A</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>22</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>24</m:mn></m:math>. Como <m:math><m:mn>22</m:mn><m:mo>≠</m:mo><m:mn>24</m:mn></m:math>, esta opción no satisface el problema.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">34<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si <m:math><m:mi>C</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>34</m:mn></m:math>, entonces <m:math><m:mi>C</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mi>V</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>34</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>44</m:mn></m:math>, pero <m:math><m:mi>A</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>22</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>24</m:mn></m:math>. Como <m:math><m:mn>44</m:mn><m:mo>≠</m:mo><m:mn>24</m:mn></m:math>, esta opción no cumple la relación.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Escribir la relación dada</strong></p>
            <p>El problema indica que se cumple:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mi>C</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mi>V</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mi>A</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p>donde <strong>C</strong> es el número de caras, <strong>V</strong> el número de vértices y <strong>A</strong> el número de aristas.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Reemplazar los datos del enunciado</strong></p>
            <p>La estructura tiene 10 uniones, es decir, <m:math><m:mi>V</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:math>.</p>
            <p>También tiene 22 barras, es decir, <m:math><m:mi>A</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>22</m:mn></m:math>.</p>
            <p>Entonces:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mi>C</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>22</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Resolver el lado derecho</strong></p>
            <p><m:math><m:mn>22</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>24</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p>Por lo tanto, la ecuación queda:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mi>C</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>24</m:mn></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Despejar el número de caras</strong></p>
            <p>Restamos 10 a ambos lados:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mi>C</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>24</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p><m:math><m:mi>C</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>14</m:mn></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La estructura tiene <strong>14 paneles planos</strong>. La alternativa correcta es <strong>B</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>